
- Use modern Python 3.12+ type hint syntax: X | Y not Union[X, Y], list[str] not List[str]
- Use Pydantic v2 API: model_validator, field_validator, ConfigDict - never use v1 @validator or class Config
- Use uv for package management in new projects - not pip or poetry
- Use pathlib.Path for all file operations - never os.path
- Use pyproject.toml for project configuration - never setup.py
